title: 267 - Stimulus Checked
description: How would you describe the health of your finances? Do you know where your money goes each month? Do you invest your money? If not, are you afraid to jump into the stock market? In this episode, the guys & guest Rob Wilson discuss money strategies, investing options, and the mindset needed to thrive in the stock market.
